com.avalara.avatax.services.tax

Class CommitTaxRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.avalara.avatax.services.tax.BaseRequest
      • com.avalara.avatax.services.tax.CommitTaxRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CommitTaxRequest
extends BaseRequest
implements java.io.Serializable
    Data to pass to TaxSvcSoap.commitTax(com.avalara.avatax.services.tax.CommitTaxRequest) indicating the document that should be committed.

    The request must specify all of getCompanyCode(), getDocCode() and getDocType() in order to uniquely identify the document.

    See Also:
    CommitTaxResult, Serialized Form
